      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tä buhß juwß uhs teem\nfazzibt: Tee Deewi/ kas to Deb-\nbefi un to Semmi ne irr darri-\nschi/ teem buhs bohjā eet no\nSemmes/ un no tchihs (Wee-\ntas/) kas appakſch Debbes irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas to Semmi irr dar-\nrijs zaur fawn Spehku/ kas to\nPafauli iſtaifijß zaur fawn Gud-\nribu/ un to Debbefi iſplattijs\nzaur fawn Saprafchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad winſch fawn Balkt-\nnt iſlaisch/ un darra dauds Uh-\nDent Debbefiß/ tad leek winſch\ntohß Twaikus uhſkahpt no\nSemmes Galleem/ winſch dar-\nra Sibbinus ar tahm Leetun/\nun leek to Wehju nahft no fa-\nweem Mantu-Kambareem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſi Zilweki irr neprat-\ntigi tappufcht ar fawn Sinna-\nschanu/ wiſſi Kaufetaji tohp\nRauna ar jawahn iſtaisitahm\nBildehm/ jo ko winſch leij/ tas\nirr Wiltiba/ un Dwaſcha ne irr\neekſch winneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee irr Neleetiba/ un\nweens wiltigajß Darbs/tai Lai-\nkā/ kad tee tohp peemekleti/ eeß\nwinni bohjā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tahds ne irr/ ka ſchee/\nkas Jehkaba Dalta irr/ jo winſch\nirr tas Taiſitajs wiſſu Leetu /\nun Iſraēts irr ta Zilts winna\nGemantoschanas/ KUNGS Ze-\npaot irr winna Wahrs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Neimun nobſt tawn Prez-\nschanu no tahs Semmes/ tu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nRangt/es gribbu tahß Semme\nEedsihwotajus schimbrithſcha-\nitt ka ar Lingut nomest/ un ap-\nbehdinaschn tohs/ ka tee to ma-\ntihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Waj man mannaß Ga-\ntreeſchanaß deht! manna Mohz-\nba irr Mohku pilna/ bet es t-\ndohmaju/ tahß irr gann Sa-\npes/ bet man tas japaneſß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Manna Buhdina it\npohſtita / un wiſtas manna-\nWirwes irr faraufitas / man-\nBehrni irr no mañini tsgabjuſch-\nun newa wairs. Neweens irr\nkas mannu Dshwokli ustaita-\nun mannas Gardines uszelf.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tee Ganni irr nepra-\ntigi tappufcht / un ne irr t-\nKUNGU meklejfcht/ tadehß ta-\nteem ne irr labbi iſdeweeg/ b-\nwiff winnu gannamajs Pu-\nirr iſkaifchts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Raugi / lahda Balkſn-\nSlanna nahß/ un leels Troh-\nnis no Seemeſa Seinnes /\nteem Pilsfahteem Juhda bu-\npohſtiteem/ un par Puhku-Ma-\nju-Weetahm tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es finnu/ af KUNGS-\nka ta Zilweka Zetſch pee win-\npascha ne stahiw/ tas ne sta-\npee lahda Wihra/ kas staiga/\ntas warretu fawu Bahjuunu p-\nreifi eetaifcht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pahrmahzi manni / KUNGS ! tomehr paanehre-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
